#########################################################################
# grimrc
#
#  Default GRIM initial settings file -
#       Each line defines a keyword value using the same syntax used on
#       IDL command line, except no quotes are used.  Lines beginning 
#       with '#' are ignored.
#
#  Copy this file into your .ominas directory and edit as desired.
#
